channel.title: A type of RuneScape 3
channel.description:
[b]Since Jagex killed RuneScape Ive been working on a private server known as "RuneScape 3rd Age." It will be a type of RuneScape 3 so to say. There is tutorial island, pking (YAY!), working on staking(ALSO YAY!, quest and most all old RuneScape 2 things. And there are no "::codes" for anyone except Game Mods. It will be as legit as the real RS2 (the one b4 Jagex ruined it). But..... I need as much help as possible to make a game such as this. I don't think I could do it all on my own (without it crashing). I need good java programmers and good MoparScape programmers. If you do decide to help make RS3A you WILL go down in all MoparScape and RuneScape history! I need you guy's help, desperately. Please do not flame me if you don't think its possible, anything and everything is possible. The server will need 4+ team members.[/b]
Sincerely, crazeyzaia. :)
